"year":-588},{"id":"recJV1qlXqtzz60XC","ref":"Jer.33.7","text":"And I will cause the captivity of Judah and the captivity of Israel to return, and will build them, as at the first.","year":-588},{"id":"recrLzg44Yki4sGIP","ref":"Jer.33.8","text":"And I will cleanse them from all their iniquity, whereby they have sinned against me; and I will pardon all their iniquities, whereby they have sinned, and whereby they have transgressed against me.","year":-588}]}
